[The good news this week is the absence of reports of newly confirmed cases of WPV1 associated paralytic disease. The not so good news are the WPV1-positive environmental samples in Pakistan, confirming that WPV1 is still circulating in the country. Other not so good news includes the 4 newly confirmed cases of cVDPV2 in the Democratic Republic of the Congo and the positive cVDPV2 environmental samples in Nigeria.

