[The above media report, while listing 7 localities in Karachi, does not give the time frame during which these specimens were collected. I chose to post this article as a reminder of what the country is facing in recent times with a growing antivaccine movement and the pre-existing and continuing violence against vaccination workers. - Mod.MPP]
